definitions.definition: Belief in the existence of at least one deity .

( strictly ) Belief in the existence of a personal creator god , goddess , gods and/or goddesses present and active in the governance and organization of the world and the universe. The God may be known by or through revelation .

main_definition: Belief in the existence of at least one deity .
secondary_definitions: ( strictly ) Belief in the existence of a personal creator god , goddess , gods and/or goddesses present and active in the governance and organization of the world and the universe. The God may be known by or through revelation .

definitions.definition: A morbid condition resulting from excessive consumption of tea .

main_definition: A morbid condition resulting from excessive consumption of tea .
